tries rely on global patriot solutions for air and missile defense our sm® missile and exoatmospheric kill vehicle defeat warheads while they’re still in space our jlens aerostats provide regional defense from  feet for  days at a time and our longrange radars keep watch around the clock from windswept stations in alaska to ships in the persian gulf it’s a big sky up there but we’ve got it covered that’s our mission learn more about our technology introduction to raytheon missile defense tracking and discrimination interception news releases newest sm interceptor aces final landbased test moves to atsea testing raytheon kill vehicle succeeds in first intercept of intercontinental ballistic missile us allies invest  million in patriot integrated air and missile defense system nextgen standard missile completes first intercept test us navy awards raytheon  million for standard missile production standard missile approved for international sales patriot nation awards raytheon more than m to upgrade missile defense system raytheon sm intercepts ballistic missile target at sea missile defense in the news raytheon to restart sm missile line after  million sale executive reuters raytheons huntsvillemade sm sm missiles take center stage at paris air show huntsville times interceptor completely obliterated mock missile pentagon says bloomberg missile takedown historic icbm intercept test sends strong message to north korea defense news missile test puts raytheon’s kill vehicle and boeing’s shield together to pulverize enemy icbms fox business raytheon wins m for multiwarhead interceptor arizona daily star raytheon to supply multiobject kill vehicle technology upi israels davids sling missile system to be operational in weeks upi the sky is not the limit the evolution of the standard missile the cipher brief usjapan antimissile test a good sign for the european missile defense sites real clear defense us japan conduct successful missile interception test cnn learn more about 